channel.title: Load Error? aka bobstarting up 20?
channel.description: Ive been using moparscape for quite a while now. I recently am using my old computer, i downloaded moparscape then was going to let it download cache. It did a common error. The error where it stops downloading cache and requests title screen and keeps failing. So then i just copied my cache from .file_store_32 and put it in .mpr_file_store_32. Then i try to boot up moparscape and after it says "starting up" it shows this. [img]http://img81.imageshack.us/img81/1333/errorrh6.jpg[/img] And this is how it looks like in the command prompt [img]http://img81.imageshack.us/img81/9169/error2eb1.jpg[/img] Someone please help me out.
